{
  "stem": "27747.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Another uncle of mine had-- had a room with two children, and another aunt lived not too far, but not-- but not in that pharmacy home.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The pharmacy was in town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the middle of town, right across from the stores.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were safe until a point.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is when they only came in and made out new documents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They selected the committee, and the committee was the one that had to deliver to them furs and jewelry from the-- from the townspeople.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The two warm fur coats of my father, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she had no fur coats, but whoever had did not hesitate to give them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A judenrat.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was several of the townspeople were in the judenrat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were selected.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As soon as the Germans came in and after the bombing-- I have to go back a little bit-- 10 of the most prominent people of Hoszcza were taken, and there were rumors that they are alive, that they're working somewhere, but very shortly we knew that on the outskirts of Hoszcza they were all killed.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think we know where the graves are, but we had an idea where they were killed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Those were not just the Nazis, not just the SS that did it, but the Ukrainians also because the prominent Jews, if they would remain, they would really, really punish them later after the war.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they made sure that none of them were alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the town had to work [INAUDIBLE] men and women.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I would say people that were of age worked in the-- in that same garrison where the park was.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
